  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] After the trial got under way-- I'd been promoted to captain-- and I was assigned my own house and had other people living with me, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was Jan Sarmas, who was a-- a refugee Czech that the Americans picked up from the Czech delegation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he later became an American, became an American professor, partly because of Colonel Storey, who-- who liked him very much.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he became a professor, first in Puerto Rico, then in Louisiana, and then in Southern Methodist University in-- in Texas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were very interesting people that you met all the way along as-- as you were doing your work in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a captain before the trial began.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the trial began on November 20, and I was a captain by then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Colonel Storey had arranged this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day he called me in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And usually I'd attend a staff conference or talk about some documents that had been found and what the labor case was and the case against the German Labor Front and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This one day I came in, and there was a circle of couple of colonels and himself and he said, sit down.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did, and I looked around, seemed funny.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he came up, and he took off my bars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought for a moment I was going to be demoted or something, and he just pinned the captain bars on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's how I knew I was being made a captain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
